  <description>
    <p>Modernised source ports of the original <em>Rise of the Triad</em> including the
      "Ludicrous Edition" add-on campaign.</p>
    <p><em>PLEASE NOTE:</em> This Flatpak does <em>not</em> include any game data.
        At least the <code>*.dmo</code>, <code>REMOTE1.RTS</code> and either the
        <code>DARKWAR.*</code> or <code>HUNTBGIN.*</code> files from a copy of
        Rise of the Triad must be copied to
        <code>$HOME/.var/app/io.github.lunarmeadow.barrett/rott/</code>.</p>
  </description>
